column5: where can I find JACKALL and EVERGREEN lures in GTA? Any suggestion guys? Thanks

Fishing Depot carries some of the Jackall stuff. Have bought TN70s from them and I am pretty sure they had the squadminnows too. Beyond them, I'm not too sure, you might have an easier time shopping online.
Never heard/seen of them before.... but would love to give them a try... How much do these JACKALL and EVERGREEN lures go for anyway?  Website?

I think OFC member Snidley also sells lures from Evergreen and Jackall as well.  Check the classifieds:   	 23 Lucky craft, 7 MegaBass plus 48 other Japanese fishinglures for sale  I've never dealt with him myself, but I'm sure there are many other OFC'ers who can vouch for him.
I will vouch for him...great guy to deal with and a definite lure junkie.  A2F: Evergreen and Jackall are like LuckyCraft, only more so. Expect to pay 25+ for hardbaits from either company.
